Command provided by: nickserv/listgroups
#endif
Help for LISTGROUPS:

LISTGROUPS shows the groups that you have access
to, including those that you own.

Group BANs are not shown.

Syntax: LISTGROUPS
#if priv group:auspex

Operators with group:auspex privilege can also
check another user's access.

Syntax: LISTGROUPS <nick>
#endif

Example:
    /msg &nick& LISTGROUPS
